Enum JSONRPC2ParamsType

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<JSONRPC2ParamsType>
      • com.thetransactioncompany.jsonrpc2.JSONRPC2ParamsType
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<JSONRPC2ParamsType>

    public enum JSONRPC2ParamsType
extends Enum<JSONRPC2ParamsType>
    Enumeration of the three parameter types in JSON-RPC 2.0 requests and notifications.
    • NO_PARAMS The method takes no parameters.
    • ARRAY The method takes positional parameters, packed as a JSON array, e.g. ["val1", "val2", ...].
    • OBJECT The method takes named parameters, packed as a JSON object, e.g. {"param1":"val1", "param2":"val2", ...}.
    Author:
    Vladimir Dzhuvinov
